title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Kingdom Technology to acquire e-commerce firm for 530 mln yuan
text:
Oct 14 Shenzhen Kingdom Technology Co Ltd
* Says plans to acquire e-commerce firm China M-World for 530 million yuan ($83.51 million) via cash
